ane.","example_es":"Necesito presentar mi tarjeta de embarque antes de abordar el avión.","example_en":"I need to show my boarding pass before boarding the plane.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a wooden board holding a pass on a tarjeta, ready for the embarque flight.","cloze_distractors_en":["Seat assignment","Luggage allowance","Flight route","Coach class"],"examples":[{"es":"Necesito presentar mi tarjeta de embarque antes de abordar el avión.","en":"I need to show my boarding pass before boarding the plane."},{"es":"Necesito imprimir mi tarjeta de embarque en el mostrador de facturación.","en":"I need to print my boarding pass at the check-in counter."},{"es":"Olvidé mi tarjeta de embarque en el control de seguridad.","en":"I forgot my boarding pass at the security checkpoint."}]},{"spanish_text":"Puerta de embarque","english_text":"Boarding gate","section_name":"Travel Phrases","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A gate or area where passengers board a plane.","main_translations_es":["Puerta de embarque"],"collocations":["boarding gate number","boarding gate location","boarding gate announcement","boarding gate time"],"synonyms_en":["departure gate","boarding area","gate"],"example_sentence":"The boarding gate for our flight to Madrid opens at 3 PM.","example_es":"La puerta de embarque para nuestro vuelo a Madrid abre a las 3 p.m.","example_en":"The boarding gate for our flight to Madrid opens at 3 PM.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a bored gate (boarding gate) swinging open like a giant puerta for the airplane.","cloze_distractors_en":["departure time","boarding pass","flight status","luggage tag"],"examples":[{"es":"La puerta de embarque para nuestro vuelo a Madrid abre a las 3 p.m.","en":"The boarding gate for our flight to Madrid opens at 3 PM."},{"es":"Nuestra puerta de embarque ha cambiado a la puerta 10.","en":"Our boarding gate has changed to gate 10."},{"es":"Por favor, diríjase a la puerta de embarque número 5.","en":"Please proceed to boarding gate number 5."}